<h1 id="toc0"><span>The passcode for being accepted to the wiki is located in the <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/guide-for-newbies" target="_blank">Guide for Newbies</a></span>. Chat Staff will not help you find it.</span></h1>
</div>
