<p>The Wiki maintains its own network of IRC servers for its users, running the latest stable versions of <a href="https://www.inspircd.org/" target="_blank">InspIRCd</a> and <a href="https://atheme.github.io/" target="_blank">Atheme</a>. We have written several guides for users to cover the new features of SkipIRC.</p>
<p><a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/skipirc:user-guide" target="_blank">SkipIRC - User Guide</a><br />
<a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/skipirc:op-guide" target="_blank">SkipIRC - Op Guide</a></p>
